Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Do you want to have a really nice feast but your table is too small?

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:11.000
We have the solution.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Today we are going to build an oak dining table for at least 6 persons.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:24.000
To do this, we will need a tabletop made of wood, board material for the table legs...

00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:31.000
...the router, the cordless screwdriver and the drill.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Have the legs cut to size at a DIY store or by a carpenter.

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:43.500
The legs each have two narrow and two wide parts,...

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:49.000
...which are joined using tongues and grooves. 

00:00:51.799 --> 00:00:58.000
In order to fit them, we first need to know which part belongs to which leg.

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:03.500
